name.zh_CN: Tabbie - 打开最近关闭的标签页
name.zh_TW: Tabbie - 打開最近關閉的分頁

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Tabbie allows you to open recently closed tabs in a simple and beautifully designed popup.
short.zh_CN: 可以让你在一个弹出窗中重新打开你最近关闭的标签页
short.zh_TW: 可以讓你在一個彈出式視窗中重新打開你最近關閉的分頁

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Tabbie allows you to undo closed tabs or windows from a simple popup.
- Beautifully designed, and supports dark mode.
- Histories of the undo tabs are saved.
- No data transmitted to third-party, privacy protected.
long.zh_CN:
Tabbie allows you to undo closed tabs or windows from a simple and elegant popup window.
- Beautifully designed, and supports dark mode.
- Histories of the undo tabs are saved.
- No data will be sent to any third-party, privacy protected.
